    "status": "Assented to. Introduced March 24, 2026; passed third reading 12-6 on March 30, 2026 and received assent. EV/e-bike rebate programs were cancelled and ~$946,000 redirected to home-heating (dual-fuel) incentives and electricity-bill relief.",
